overview: PROGRESS Wrestling will present Chapter 105: Bring The Thunder on Saturday, February 27th on the WWE Network and Demand PROGRESS from the Theatre Peckham in London, England, with the event to feature the culmination of the Natural Progression Series 7 that will kick off this Saturday on the WWE Network and Demand PROGRESS, while the main event will feature the first-ever Female ThunderBastard Match.
title: PROGRESS Chapter 105: Bring The Thunder
